      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so quiet here. i spend 10 hours a day staring at a screen in this apartment and the only time anyone \"interacts\" with me is through a slack notification or a brief email. sometimes i feel like if i just stopped logging on, or if i just wasn't here, the world would just keep spinning like nothing even happened. like i'm just a ghost in the machine.",
