      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... i don't think there's anyone to tell. i look at my contact list and it's all just work stuff. people i might have known years ago but now we're just digital traces. if i just... stopped. if i just disappeared from all the feeds and the chats, i don't think there would even be a ripple. it would just be a quiet gap that gets filled by something else immediately. it feels like i'm already gone, just waiting for my body to catch up.",
